jwsung91-unilink is deprecated. Use wirestead instead:

    find_package(wirestead CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE wirestead::wirestead)

This compatibility port depends on wirestead, which still installs the legacy
UniLink CMake package for v0.9.x source compatibility:

    find_package(unilink CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE unilink::unilink)
